#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:7
msgid "Digital Inclusion: Vital to Internet Health"
msgstr "Cynhwysiad Digidol: Yn Hanfodol ar gyfer Iechyd y Rhyngrwyd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:11
msgid ""
"Digital inclusion means promoting diversity, practicing respect, and "
"supporting universal access online."
msgstr ""
"Mae cynhwysiad digidol yn golygu hyrwyddo amrywiaeth, ymarfer parch a "
"chefnogi mynediad i bawb ar-lein."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:15
msgid "Privacy &amp; Security"
msgstr "Preifatrwydd a Diogelwch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:19
msgid "Open Innovation"
msgstr "Arloesi Agored"

#. # TAG: health-decentralization-and-literacy
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:24
msgid "Decentralization"
msgstr "Datganoli"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:28
msgid "Digital Inclusion"
msgstr "Cynhwysiad Digidol"

#. # TAG: health-decentralization-and-literacy
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:33
msgid "Web Literacy"
msgstr "Llythrennedd Gwe"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:37
msgid "A Healthy Internet is Inclusive to All"
msgstr "Mae Rhyngrwyd Iach yn Cynnwys Pawb"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:41
msgid ""
"The more voices, perspective, languages, and people contributing to the Web, "
"the richer the experience for everyone. But the whole Internet is not yet "
"accessible, welcoming, and safe for all. Together, we have the power to "
"shape the Web, and our world along with it."
msgstr ""
"Po fwyaf o leisiau, safbwyntiau, ieithoedd a phobl sy'n cyfrannu i'r We, y "
"mwyaf cyfoethog fydd y profiad i bawb. Ond nid yw'r holl ryngrwyd ar gael, "
"yn groesawgar nac yn ddiogel ar gyfer pawb. Gyda'n gilydd, mae gennym y grym "
"i siapio'r We, a'n byd ni hefyd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:45
msgid "A healthy Internet is open to you."
msgstr "‌Mae Rhyngrwyd iach ar agor i chi."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:49
msgid "Here are three areas where we can make a difference."
msgstr "Dyma dri maes lle gallwn ni wneud gwahaniaeth."

#. This is a navigation link
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:54
msgid "Promote Diversity"
msgstr "Hyrwyddo Amrywiaeth"

#. This is a navigation link
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:59
msgid "Practice Respect"
msgstr "Ymarfer Parch"

#. This is a navigation link
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:64
msgid "Support Universal Access"
msgstr "Cefnogi Mynediad Cyffredinol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:68
msgid "Digital Inclusion means promoting diversity"
msgstr "Mae Cynhwysiad Digidol yn golygu hyrwyddo arywiaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:72
msgid ""
"For the Internet to fulfill its greatest promise, it must reflect the "
"diversity and experience of all people, everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn i'r Rhyngrwyd gyflawni ei addewid yn llawn, mae'n rhaid iddo "
"adlewyrchu amrywiaeth a phrofiad pawb, ymhob man."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:76
msgid ""
"As inclusive as the Web can seem, it’s not yet an equal playing field. More "
"than half the world is still without it; emerging economies and marginalized "
"communities are often the last to gain access. Far fewer women are using the "
"Internet than men. And without diversity among its creators, the Web itself "
"will reflect unconscious biases, while personalizing algorithms can "
"reinforce our own."
msgstr ""
"Er fod y We'n ymddangos yn gynhwysol, nid yw eto'n faes chwarae cyfartal. "
"Nid yw ar gael i fwy na hanner y byd; yr olaf i gael mynediad yw economïau "
"sy'n datblygu a chymunedau ymylol. Mae llawer llai o ferched na dynion yn "
"defnyddio'r rhyngrwyd. A heb amrywiaeth ymysg y rhai sy'n creu cynnwys, bydd "
"y We'n adlewyrchu tueddiadau difeddwl, tra bod algorithmau personoli'n "
"atgyfnerthu ein rhai ni ein hunain."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:80
msgid ""
"In nine developing countries, women are still nearly 50% less likely to "
"access the Internet than men."
msgstr ""
"Mewn naw gwlad sy'n datblygu, mae merched yn 50% llai tebygol i fynd ar y we "
"na dynion."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:84
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(wwwf)s\">World Wide Web Foundation</a>, 2015"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(wwwf)s\">World Wide Web Foundation</a>, 2015"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box.
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:89
msgid "50%"
msgstr "50%"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:93
msgid "How you can promote diversity"
msgstr "Sut mae modd hyrwyddo amrywiaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:97
msgid "Create web content"
msgstr "Creu cynnwys gwe"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:101
msgid ""
"Create your own Web content – like videos, blog posts, GIFs – in your "
"language, local to your area."
msgstr ""
"Creu eich cynnwys Gwe – fideos, cofnodion blog, GIFau – yn eich iaith, yn "
"lleol i'ch ardal."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:105
msgid "Build resources"
msgstr "Adeiladu adnoddau"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:109
msgid ""
"Support a resource like <a href=\"%(wiki_support)s\">Wikipedia</a> that "
"drastically lowers the barriers to knowledge – or better yet, <a href="
"\"%(wiki_contribute)s\">help build it</a>. Wikipedia needs more, and more "
"diverse, contributors."
msgstr ""
"Cefnogwch adnodd fel <a href=\"%(wiki_support)s\">Wikipedia</a> sy'n "
"lleihau'r rhwystrau i addysg yn sylweddol – neu hyd yn oed yn well, <a href="
"\"%(wiki_contribute)s\">cynorthwywch i'w adeiladu</a>. Mae Wikipedia angen "
"rhagor o gyfranwyr a rhagor o amrywiaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:113
msgid "How Mozilla is promoting diversity"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n hyrwyddo amrywiaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:117
msgid "Advancing accessibility"
msgstr "Hyrwyddo mynediad"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:121
msgid ""
"Advancing web accessibility standards, and making Firefox inclusive through "
"efforts like our <a href=\"%(web_a11y)s\">Accessibility</a> team."
msgstr ""
"Amlygu safonau hygyrchedd gwe a gwneud Firefox yn gynhwysol drwy ymdrechion "
"fel ein tîm <a href=\"%(web_a11y)s\">Hygyrchedd</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:125
msgid "Building digital skills"
msgstr "Adeiladu sgiliau digidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:129
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(un_women)s\">Partnering with UN Women</a> to help women in "
"Africa and across the globe build key digital skills."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"%(un_women)s\">Partnering with UN Women</a> i gynorthwyo merched "
"yn Affrica ac ar draws y byd i adeiladu sgiliau digidol allweddol."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:133
msgid "Digital Inclusion means practicing respect"
msgstr "Mae Cynhwysiad Digidol yn golygu ymarfer parch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:137
msgid ""
"We should all have the ability to participate fully on the Internet, without "
"threat to our reputations, our confidence, or our safety."
msgstr ""
"Dylai pawb fod â'r gallu i gymryd rhan yn llawn ar y Rhyngrwyd heb fygythiad "
"i'n henw da, ein hyder na'n diogelwch."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:141
msgid ""
"We’ve all seen our share of nasty comments sections. At times, the Web can "
"feel like a very unfriendly place – particularly for women, minorities, and "
"members of marginalized communities. By discouraging people from getting "
"online, cyberbullying and cyber violence threaten not just individuals, but "
"the Internet itself."
msgstr ""
"Rydym i gyd wedi gweld adrannau sylwadau cas. Ar adegau, mae'r we'n gallu "
"teimlo fel lle anghyfeillgar iawn – yn arbennig ar gyfer merched ac aelodau "
"o gymunedau ymylol. Drwy annog pobl rhag mynd ar lein, bwlio ar-lein a "
"thrais sebr mae'n fygythiadau nid yn unig i unigolion ond i'r Rhyngrwyd ei "
"hun."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:145
msgid ""
"73% of Internet users have seen someone harassed online and 40% have "
"personally experienced it."
msgstr ""
"Mae 73% o ddefnyddwyr y Rhyngrwyd wedi gweld rhywun yn cael ei aflonyddu ar-"
"lein ac mae 40% wedi ei brofi'n bersonol."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:149
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(pew)s\">Pew Research</a>, 2014"
msgstr "Ffynhonell: <a href=\"%(pew)s\">Pew Research</a>, 2014"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box.
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:154
msgid "73%"
msgstr "73%"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:158
msgid "How you can practice respect"
msgstr "Sut mae arfer parch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:162
msgid "Report bullying"
msgstr "Adrodd ar fwlio"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:166
msgid ""
"If you see cyber violence and bullying online, <a href=\"%(report)s\">record "
"it and report it</a>."
msgstr ""
"Os fyddwch yn gweld trais seibr a bwlio ar-lein, <a href=\"%(report)s"
"\">gwnewch gofnod a'i adrodd</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:170
msgid "Talk about respect"
msgstr "Siarad yn barchus"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:174
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(kids)s\">Talk to your kids</a> about cyberbullying, and <a href="
"\"%(teachers)s\">encourage their teachers to do the same</a>."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"%(kids)s\">Siaradwch â'ch plant</a> am fwlio seibr, ac <a href="
"\"%(teachers)s\">annog eu hathrawon i wneud yr un peth</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:178
msgid "How Mozilla is practicing respect"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n arfer parch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:182
msgid "Supporting tools for safety"
msgstr "Cefnogi offer ar gyfer diogelwch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:186
msgid ""
"Supporting the <a href=\"%(coral)s\">Coral Project</a>, which works to "
"improve how journalists and communities engage on news websites, including "
"tools like <a href=\"%(talk)s\">Talk</a>, that aims to create smarter, safer "
"comments sections."
msgstr ""
"Cefnogi'r <a href=\"%(coral)s\">Coral Project</a>, sy'n gweithio i wella sut "
"mae newyddiadurwyr a chymunedau'n ymwneud a'i gilydd ar wefannau newyddion, "
"cynnwys offer fel <a href=\"%(talk)s\">Talk</a>, sy'n anelu at greu adrannau "
"sylwadau mwy clyfar a diogel."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:190
msgid "Empowering individuals"
msgstr "Grymuso unigolion"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:194
msgid ""
"Creating open curricula that empowers people to create safe spaces online, "
"like the <a href=\"%(teaching)s\">Teaching Kit: Combating Cyber Violence "
"Against Women and Girls</a>."
msgstr ""
"Creu meysydd llafur agored sy'n grymuso pobl i greu mannau diogel ar-lein, "
"fel y <a href=\"%(teaching)s\">Teaching Kit: Combating Cyber Violence "
"Against Women and Girls</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:198
msgid ""
"Digital Inclusion means supporting universal access to the whole Internet"
msgstr ""
"Mae Cynhwysiad Digidol yn golygu cynnal mynediad cyffredinol i'r Rhyngrwyd i "
"gyd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:202
msgid ""
"We should all have affordable, high-quality, unrestricted access to the "
"whole Web, so the whole world can benefit."
msgstr ""
"Dylai pawb fod â mynediad pris rhesymol, ansawdd uchel a heb gyfyngiad i'r "
"holl We, er mantais i'r byd i gyd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:206
msgid ""
"To participate online, you have to be able to get online. Programs have "
"emerged that offer free or subsidized Internet access, but it is often slow "
"or restricted, creating a ‘poor Internet for poor people.’ At its most "
"extreme, governments worldwide are turning off all or parts of the Internet "
"to serve their own agendas, which can threaten human rights and even the "
"health of the global economy."
msgstr ""
"I gymryd rhan ar-lein, mae'n rhaid eich bod yn gallu mynd ar-lein. Mae "
"rhaglenni wedi ymddangos sy'n cynnig mynediad i'r Rhyngrwyd am ddim neu wedi "
"eu cymorthdalu, ond mae'n aml yn araf neu wedi ei gyfyngu, gan greu "
"'rhyngrwyd sâl ar gyfer pobl dlawd'. Mewn enghreifftiau eithafol, mae rhai "
"llywodraethau ar draws y byd yn diffodd rhan neu'r We i gyd er mwyn eu "
"hagenda eu hunain, sy'n bygwth hawliau dynol a hyd yn oed iechyd yr economi "
"byd-eang."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:210
msgid "In 2016, there were 51 intentional Internet shutdowns in 18 countries."
msgstr ""
"Yn 2016, cafodd y Rhyngrwyd ei ddiffodd yn fwriadol 51 gwaith mewn 18 gwlad."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:214
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(accessnow)s\">AccessNow</a>, 2016"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(accessnow)s\">AccessNow</a>, 2016"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box.
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:219
msgid "51"
msgstr "51"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:223
msgid "How you can support universal access"
msgstr "Sut fedrwch chi gefnogi mynediad cyffredinol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:227
msgid "Donate your tech"
msgstr "Cyfrannu eich offer"

#. # TAG: inclusion-donate-tech
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:232
msgid ""
"Donate your old computers, laptops, and phones to non-profits that refurbish "
"and redistribute them to underserved communities."
msgstr ""
"Rhowch eich hen gyfrifiaduron, gliniaduron a ffonau i gyrff ddim-er-elw i'w "
"hadnewyddu a'u hailddosbarthu i gymunedau difreintiedig."

#. String is obsolete. Do NOT remove.
#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:237
msgid ""
"Donate your old computers, laptops, and phones to non-profits like <a href="
"\"%(reconnect)s\">Reconnect</a>, <a href=\"%(strut)s\">Students Recycling "
"Used Technology</a>, or <a href=\"%(interconnection)s\">Interconnection</a>, "
"who refurbish and redistribute them to underserved communities."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch gyfrannu eich hen gyfrifiaduron, gliniaduron a ffonau i gyrff dim-er-"
"elw fel i <a href=\"%(reconnect)s\">Reconnect</a>, <a href=\"%(strut)s"
"\">Students Recycling Used Technology</a>, or <a href=\"%(interconnection)s"
"\">Interconnection</a> sy'n eu trwsio a'u hailddosbarthu i gymunedau llai "
"breintiedig."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:241
msgid "Advocate for openness"
msgstr "Eirioli er mwyn bod yn agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:245
msgid ""
"Tell your representatives that open and affordable access to the Internet "
"should be a policy priority."
msgstr ""
"Dywedwch wrth eich aelodau cynulliad a seneddol y dylai mynediad agored a "
"fforddiadwy fod yn flaenoriaeth polisi."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:249
msgid "How Mozilla is supporting universal access"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n cefnogi mynediad cyffredinol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:253
msgid "Advocating for neutrality"
msgstr "Eirioli o blaid niwtraliaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:257
msgid ""
"Championing <a href=\"%(neutrality)s\">net neutrality</a>, so that everyone "
"has access to the same Internet."
msgstr ""
"Bod yn bencampwr <a href=\"%(neutrality)s\">niwtraliaeth y rhyngrwyd</a>, "
"fel bod pawb yn cael mynediad i'r un Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:261
msgid "Connecting the unconnected"
msgstr "Cysylltu'r rhai sydd heb eu cysylltu"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:265
msgid ""
"Sponsoring the <a href=\"%(equalrating)s\">Equal Rating Innovation "
"Challenge</a> to find novel solutions for connecting the unconnected to the "
"full, open Internet."
msgstr ""
"Noddi'r <a href=\"%(equalrating)s\">Equal Rating Innovation Challenge</a> er "
"mwyn darganfod atebion newydd ar gyfer cysylltu'r rhai sydd heb eu cysylltu "
"i'r Rhyngrwyd llawn ac agored."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:269
msgid "Hungry for more?"
msgstr "Eisiau gwybod rhagor?"

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:273
msgid ""
"Read on about Digital Inclusion in our <a href=\"%(healthreport)s\">Internet "
"Health Report</a>."
msgstr ""
"Rhagor am Gynhwysiad Digidol yn ein <a href=\"%(healthreport)s\">Internet "
"Health Report</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:277
msgid "Stay informed."
msgstr "Derbyn gwybodaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/digital-inclusion.lang:281
msgid ""
"Sign up. Read up. Get the Mozilla newsletter to stay smart on the issues "
"affecting your life online."
msgstr ""
"Ymunwch. Darllenwch. Gallwch dderbyn cylchlythyr Mozilla er mwyn deall yn "
"well am faterion sy'n effeithio ar eich bywyd ar-lein."
